et in Idumota, Lagos Island, is facing a three-count charge of conspiracy, importation of… October 24, 2019 In "News" A 39-year-old unemployed man Michael Oloniluyi, was, yesterday, arraigned before an Ikeja Magistrate’s Court for allegedly impersonating a police officer. March 31, 2014 In "News" A 30-year-old blacksmith, Pius Itodo, was Tuesday arraigned before a Lagos Magistrate's Court, sitting in Ikeja, for allegedly presenting himself as a police officer. July 9, 2013 In "News"